ItemDisplay[amu ILVL>79 MAG]: %PURPLE% § [Ya!!Magic-NODE] %BLUE%%NAME% %WHITE%L%ILVL% %PURPLE%§{%TAN%Craft at clvl 86+ for +2 Skills%NL%%ORANGE%Caster: P Ame + Ral + Jewel} %TIER-9%
ItemDisplay[amu ILVL>79 RARE]: %PURPLE%§ [Ya!!Rare] § %NL%%WHITE%%NAME% L%ILVL% %PURPLE% %TIER-9%

